### 6. PyTorch Tensors

Studied the core data structure used throughout PyTorch.

Learned how to create tensors:

#### From Python Lists

```python
torch.tensor(data)
```

#### From NumPy Arrays

```python
torch.from_numpy(array)
```

#### Random Tensors

```python
torch.rand(shape)
```

#### Ones and Zeros

```python
torch.ones(shape)
torch.zeros(shape)
```

